# Design Doc Routing

Use `docs/design/README.md` as the routing index.

Default:
- For local refactor, bugfix, and test-cleanup tasks, start from touched code/tests and the matching local skill.
- Do not auto-load `docs/design/core-architecture.md` for local refactor/test-only work.

Load `docs/design/core-architecture.md` only for:
- new features
- cross-domain wiring
- save/events/persistence changes
- cases where local code intent is unclear
